details.title: Industry Speaker Event - Alumni Insights: Lessons in AI & Life
details.longDescription: Join us for an inspiring industry speaker event where alumni share their experiences in AI, the lessons they’ve learned throughout their careers, and insights on navigating professional and personal growth. This event is perfect for anyone interested in AI, career development, and learning from real-world experiences.
